  "title": "Interior Designer",
  "description": "<p><strong>🎨 Interior Design Consultant</strong></p><p><em>Bring dreams to life, one space at a time.</em></p><p><strong>We’re not just designing spaces — we’re crafting lifestyles.</strong><br />If you’re a people person with a flair for design and love the thrill of seeing ideas become reality, this one’s for you!</p><p><strong>💼 Your Role:</strong></p><p>As our Interior Design Consultant, you’ll be the bridge between creativity and client's dreams. From the first hello to project handover, you’ll be guiding homeowners and business owners through a journey of style, comfort, and function — all while hitting those sales goals like a pro.</p><p><strong>✨ What You'll Be Doing:</strong></p><ul><li>🎯 Translate client vibes into stylish, functional design solutions.</li><li>💡 Present space plans and concept boards with confidence and flair.</li><li>🧩 Collaborate with our design squad + contractors to make the magic happen.</li><li>📞 Keep clients updated and smiling from kickoff to completion.</li><li>📝 Provide regular project updates to our Director (bonus points if they’re impressive!)</li></ul><p><strong>🧠 What We’re Looking For:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Interior Design (or a similar field).</li><li>Ideally 1 year of experience, but fresh grads with mad passion are welcome too!</li><li>AutoCAD, Photoshop, PowerPoint – you're fluent in these, or close to it.</li><li>Great with people? Even better with sales? We want your energy!</li><li>Detail-oriented, proactive, and ready to shine in a fast-paced team.</li></ul><p>🌟 Why Join Us?</p><ul><li>Positive vibes only — we’re big on collaboration, fun, and celebrating wins.</li><li>Transparent commissions + potential higher pay for experienced talents.</li><li>Supportive culture that values <strong>attitude, not just your résumé</strong>.</li><li>Creative freedom to express your design personality.</li></ul><p><em>“Hire for attitude, not just experience.” – Greg Savage</em></p><p><em>Interested applicant may click \"Apply\" for this role or send your resume to career@mrshopperstudio.com</em></p>",
